# Network Commands Cheat Sheet

## Connectivity

| Command | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| ping | Test connectivity |
| tracert / traceroute | Show packet path |
| pathping | Ping + Traceroute |

---

## IP Configuration

Windows

ipconfig

ipconfig /all

ipconfig /release

ipconfig /renew

ipconfig /flushdns

Linux

ifconfig

ip addr

---

## DNS

nslookup google.com

dig google.com

host google.com

---

## ARP

arp -a

Displays ARP Cache.

---

## Routing

route print

route -n

ip route

---

## Active Connections

netstat -an

ss -tuln

---

## MAC Address

getmac

ip link

---

## Interface Information

